<p>If you click the ugly link above you should see a a bar that resembles something close to this:</p>
<p><img src="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/5510475/Screen%20Shot%202011-09-27%20at%2012.58.49%20PM.png" alt="" width="764" height="199" /></p>
<p>You should be able to select the "Add new" drop down and add a page. It's a little messy and I don't consider this to be ready for primetime but it should work. There is more information available here:&nbsp;<a href="http://plone.org/documentation/manual/plone-4-user-manual/adding-content/adding-pages">http://plone.org/documentation/manual/plone-4-user-manual/adding-content/adding-pages</a></p>